Reminds me of Binary but not a match

[http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/binary-itc/](http://web.archive.org/web/20131012062634/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/binary-itc/ "http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/linotype/binary-itc/")
Thanks Pattyfab. It's good to know about Binary. Any other takers?

So, I'm coming to the conclusion that this must be custom. There have been 148 reads and no conclusive font. This must mean it's custom.

Binary is looking better and better all the time! :-)

Thanks all for playing.
Has some resemblance to an customised and anemic Times New Roman.
